WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.615
To view the current connections on your set OS distro,

00:00:03.615 --> 00:00:09.340
connect via SSH and type netstat space minus at.

00:00:09.890 --> 00:00:13.845
As you can see, there's not many connections at the moment.

00:00:13.845 --> 00:00:18.030
Let's take a look at the routing table type netstat space minus

00:00:18.030 --> 00:00:24.570
r. Here you see information on how this machine connects with the outside world.

00:00:24.570 --> 00:00:27.240
To view only the ports listening to traffic,

00:00:27.240 --> 00:00:33.615
type netstat space minus l. To view all of the current SSH connections,

00:00:33.615 --> 00:00:41.530
type netstat space minus atep pipe, grep ssh.

